{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Greedy Misadventure</h2>Embark on a whirlwind adventure in SCRAM!, a heart-pounding, fast-paced platformer that brings players into the world of Boki, a cunning and sprightly goblin with an insatiable thirst for treasure and chaos. The game centers around mesmerizing levels, reaching top speeds, and toppling colossal bosses while navigating the lush worlds and engaging challenges.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PLATFORMING AT ITS BEST</h2>With lightning reflexes and boundless energy, guide Boki through a series of pulse-pounding levels filled with pitfalls, enemies, and treasures waiting to be claimed.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486570/extras/PlatformingRedone.gif?t=1722963400\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">NEED FOR SPEED</h2>Speed is the ultimate ally. Dodge obstacles and slash enemies to reach MAX speed as you traverse thrilling levels with non-stop challenges.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486570/extras/LookaheadCameraRedone.gif?t=1722963400\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STUNNING LANDSCAPES</h2>Journey through enchanting levels across varied worlds, including Dreadfire's Keep, Petrifying Forest, and Ruined Bastion.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486570/extras/BeautifulBackgrounds.gif?t=1722963400\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MASSIVE BOSS BATTLES</h2>Colossal bosses stand in the way of new areas and precious treasure, each one tougher with unique attack patterns.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486570/extras/BossRedone.gif?t=1722963400\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Perfect Run","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2486570/1b5a947cca689816dc6ddd7e6b4117116723ab4a.jpg"},{"name":"Getting BETTER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.ste